#. <section class="sutta" id="sn47.31"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.31:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: 4. Ananussutavagga → anussutaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn47.31:0.2"
msgid "4. Ananussutavagga"
msgstr "4. Not Learned From Anyone Else"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 31. Ananussutasutta → anussutavaggo (pts1)
msgctxt "sn47.31:0.3"
msgid "31. Ananussutasutta"
msgstr "31. Not Learned From Anyone Else"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.179"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.31:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn47.31:1.2"
msgid ""
"“‘Ayaṃ kāye kāyānupassanā’ti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu "
"cakkhuṃ udapādi, ñāṇaṃ udapādi, paññā udapādi, vijjā udapādi, āloko udapādi."
msgstr ""
"“‘This is the observation of an aspect of the body.’ Such, mendicants, was "
"the vision, knowledge, wisdom, realization, and light that arose in me "
"regarding teachings not learned before from another."

msgctxt "sn47.31:1.3"
msgid "‘Sā kho panāyaṃ kāye kāyānupassanā bhāvetabbā’ti me, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr "‘This observation of an aspect of the body should be developed.’ …"

msgctxt "sn47.31:1.4"
msgid ""
"bhāvitā’ti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṃ udapādi, ñāṇaṃ "
"udapādi, paññā udapādi, vijjā udapādi, āloko udapādi."
msgstr ""
"‘This observation of an aspect of the body has been developed.’ Such was the "
"vision, knowledge, wisdom, realization, and light that arose in me regarding "
"teachings not learned before from another."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.31:2.1"
msgid ""
"‘Ayaṃ vedanāsu vedanānupassanā’ti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu "
"cakkhuṃ udapādi, ñāṇaṃ udapādi, paññā udapādi, vijjā udapādi, āloko udapādi."
msgstr "‘This is the observation of an aspect of feelings.’ …"

msgctxt "sn47.31:2.2"
msgid ""
"‘Sā kho panāyaṃ vedanāsu vedanānupassanā bhāvetabbā’ti me, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr "‘This observation of an aspect of feelings should be developed.’ …"

msgctxt "sn47.31:2.3"
msgid ""
"bhāvitā’ti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṃ udapādi, ñāṇaṃ "
"udapādi, paññā udapādi, vijjā udapādi, āloko udapādi."
msgstr "‘This observation of an aspect of feelings has been developed.’ …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.31:3.1"
msgid ""
"‘Ayaṃ citte cittānupassanā’ti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu "
"cakkhuṃ udapādi, ñāṇaṃ udapādi, paññā udapādi, vijjā udapādi, āloko udapādi."
msgstr "‘This is the observation of an aspect of the mind.’ …"

msgctxt "sn47.31:3.2"
msgid "‘Sā kho panāyaṃ citte cittānupassanā bhāvetabbā’ti me, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr "‘This observation of an aspect of the mind should be developed.’ …"

msgctxt "sn47.31:3.3"
msgid ""
"bhāvitā’ti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṃ udapādi, ñāṇaṃ "
"udapādi, paññā udapādi, vijjā udapādi, āloko udapādi."
msgstr "‘This observation of an aspect of the mind has been developed.’ …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.31:4.1"
msgid ""
"‘Ayaṃ dhammesu dhammānupassanā’ti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu "
"cakkhuṃ udapādi, ñāṇaṃ udapādi, paññā udapādi, vijjā udapādi, āloko udapādi."
msgstr "‘This is the observation of an aspect of principles.’ …"

msgctxt "sn47.31:4.2"
msgid ""
"‘Sā kho panāyaṃ dhammesu dhammānupassanā bhāvetabbā’ti me, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr "‘This observation of an aspect of principles should be developed.’ …"

msgctxt "sn47.31:4.3"
msgid ""
"bhāvitā’ti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṃ udapādi, ñāṇaṃ "
"udapādi, paññā udapādi, vijjā udapādi, āloko udapādī”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘This observation of an aspect of principles has been developed.’ Such was "
"the vision, knowledge, wisdom, realization, and light that arose in me "
"regarding teachings not learned before from another.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.31:4.4"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
